module counter_logic(
    input rst_n,
    input clk,
    input valid_count,
    output [3:0] count
);
    reg [3:0] count;

    always @(posedge clk or posedge rst_n) begin
        if (rst_n == 1) begin
            count <= 4'b00000;
        end
        else begin
            if (valid_count == 1) begin
                count <= count + 1;
            end
        end
    end

    assign out = count;

endmodule

module waveform_generator(
    input clk,
    input rst_n,
    output wave
);
    reg [4:0] wave;

    always @(posedge clk or negedge rst_n)
    begin
        if(~rst_n)
            wave <= 0;
        else
            if(wave == 31)
                wave <= 0;
            else
                wave <= wave + 1;
    end
    assign waveform = wave;

endmodule
